---
---
<section class="py-24 sm:py-36 px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-14 bg-[var(--color-soft)] relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 sm:gap-10 items-center">
    <!-- Text side (visual left in RTL = first in DOM) -->
    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 reveal order-2 lg:order-1">
      <div class="ltr text-[11px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[var(--color-coral)] font-medium mb-4">— A Personal Invite</div>
      <div class="font-poster text-[var(--color-coral)] text-5xl sm:text-7xl leading-none mb-6">05</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-[var(--color-ink)] leading-[1.05]">
        שמעו<br/>מ<em class="not-italic text-[var(--color-coral)]">יעל</em>.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-[var(--color-muted)] text-lg leading-relaxed">
        תכניסו אוזניות. יעל מספרת על הקהילה,
        על האנשים, ולמה שווה להיכנס פנימה.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-[var(--color-ink)]">
        <span class="text-2xl">↓</span>
        <span class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">אז מוכנים?</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Video side -->
    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 reveal order-1 lg:order-2">
      <div class="relative rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-[var(--color-ink)]">
        <video
          src="/images/video.mp4"
          controls
          playsinline
          preload="metadata"
          poster="/images/IMG_4498.jpg"
          class="w-full h-auto block"
        >
          הדפדפן שלך לא תומך בנגן וידאו.
        </video>
        <!-- Editorial frame caption -->
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-3 ltr text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[var(--color-soft)]/85 bg-[var(--color-ink)]/40 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
          ★ Yael · TLV Young
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
